The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves hypergraph partitioning algorithms (cs.DS), revenue maximization (cs.EC), and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper uses a duality framework developed in a previous paper (cs.LG).
